caption: Table 1: The accuracy (%) and the average time consumption (seconds) of the based model and the model optimized by out methods on gsm8k and MATH.
description: This table presents a comparison of the performance of a baseline language model and a model enhanced by the proposed method.  The comparison is done across two benchmark datasets (gsm8k and MATH), showing both accuracy percentages and average inference time (in seconds).  This allows for an evaluation of the trade-off between improved accuracy and increased processing time resulting from the optimization technique.
